I"2	<p>I consider my teachers to be the people who influenced me the most throughout my life. They helped me grow and become a better version of myself and therefore I feel that by teaching others, I can help them do the same. Based on these interactions, my philosophy of teaching resonates with Socrates’ as I believe in making my students question and possibly re-invent the material they are learning.</p>

